e at runtime.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No Docker image, environment variable, or system property appears necessary. If generated tests exercise Activator/OsgiRegistry, use lightweight Bundle/BundleContext fakes or mocks; no running OSGi container is required.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"If both the old osgi_R4_core API jar and the newer OSGi API jar are present, duplicated org.osgi.framework classes could hide API mismatches; generated tests should target the API level required by jersey-core 1.14.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02da36dc11649ec8016a42e30bf7788196942d4bd2c8113232\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 647, "output": 795, "cacheRead": 23040, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 24482, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782768385584, "responseId": "resp_02da36dc11649ec8016a42e30204a88196bd428b67b35ddb13"}}
